### Hadith 1:444

*Narrated Hassan bin Thabit Al-Ansari:*

I asked Abu Huraira "By Allah! Tell me the truth whether you heard the
Prophet saying, 'O Hassan! Reply on behalf of Allah's Apostle. O Allah!
Help him with the Holy Spirit." Abu Huraira said, "Yes . "

